---
// Componente Hero institucional para Colegio Alpha
---
<section id="inicio" class="pt-28 pb-16   bg-gradient-to-br  relative overflow-hidden ">
  <div class="absolute h-screen inset-0  w-full  bg-center bg-cover filter brightness-105  z-10" style="background-image: url('Hero2.jpg');"></div>
  <div class="absolute h-screeninset-0 bg-white/50  "></div>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row  gap-10 px-4">
    
    <div class="flex-1 flex justify-start md:justify-start animate-fade-in">
      
    </div>
    <div class="flex-1 text-center md:text-right z-20  rounded-2xl">
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-end items-end">
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
          <img src="/logo.webp" alt="Logo Colegio Alpha" class=" size-56 md:size-32 drop-shadow-[10px_15px_15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] z-20" />
          <h1 class="uppercase text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-[var(--steam-azul-oscuro)] mb-4 leading-tight animate-fade-in-up drop-shadow-[0px_15px_50px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)]">Colegio Alpha</Fragment>
        </div>
        <p class="text-2xl md:text-4xl text-[var(--steam-verde)] | font-bold mb-4 animate-fade-in-up delay-100 drop-shadow-[0px_15px_15px_rgba(255,255,255,1)]">de Pachuca</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center   rounded-2xl p-4 backdrop-blur-sm mb-8">
        <p class="text-lg text-[#002444]  font-bold  animate-fade-in-up delay-300">En Colegio Alpha de Pachuca nos comprometemos con la formación integral de tus hijos, desarrollando sus habilidades en entornos científicos y tecnológicos con valores.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center sm:flex-row gap-4 animate-fade-in-up delay-400">
        <a href="#inscripcion" class="inline-block bg-[var(--color-logo-azul)] text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold text-lg shadow-lg hover:bg-[var(--color-logo-verde)] hover:text-white transition">¡Inscríbete hoy!</a>
        <a href="#filosofia" class="inline-block bg-white text-[var(--color-logo-azul)] px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold text-lg shadow-lg border-2 border-[var(--color-logo-azul)] hover:bg-[var(--color-logo-azul)] hover:text-white transition">Conoce más</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    
  </div>
</section> 